       Aracnia felt a sudden burst of relief. The spark had left her body, 
and now a system of repair took over he main programming, slipping her into a 
state of stasis. She didnt get to see her offspring, not yet at least.

       Megatron lumbered through the darkness of the ship. Bored, and with 
angry troops, he needed to do something. Kitkat, obviously, was more 
concerned with her own agenda. Meanwhile, the Maximals and the Allience 
parade all over Prehistoric earth. He needed to contact someone....things 
needed to change.

--part1_f5.4f86c4b.2755ae17_boundary
